---
layout: post
title: "combining LaTeX, pythonTeX, and siunix"
date: 2018-10-16
---
Combining LaTeX (and XeTeX etc) with python to make for (a) reproducable papers etc., and (b) making exam question setting and solutions more reliable.

The package pythontex is the key. It is available on CTAN.

With this can insert blocks of python into LaTeX document.
